<p>These yield the systems (axioms in bold, systems in italics):
</p>
<ul><li><i>K</i>&nbsp;:=3D <b>K</b> + <b>N</b></li>
<li><i>T</i>&nbsp;:=3D <i>K</i> + <b>T</b></li>
