-align: -0.338ex; width:8.397ex; height:2.176ex;" alt=3D"{\displaystyle \Bo=
x P=3DP}"></span> is the case at every time <i>t</i></dd></dl>
<p>Or we can trade these operators to deal only with the future (or past). =
For example,
</p>
<dl><dd><span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span clas=
