-align: -0.838ex; width:20.407ex; height:2.843ex;" alt=3D"{\displaystyle \D=
iamond _{2}P=3DP{\text{ and}}{/}{\text{or }}{\mathsf {F}}P}"></span></dd>
<dd><span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span class=3D=
"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;"><mat=
h xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext=3D"{\displaystyle \B=
ox _{2}P=3DP{\text{ and }}{\mathsf {G}}P}">
